reviewText:
Supercross/Motocross is always great to watch, and these riders are amazing.  But there is way too much of the biography/interview BS on this that we've already seen on ESPN.  Just show me the best of the racing!

If you've seen ESPN broadcasts of supercross already, you don't need to see this.

BTW, when are we going to get DVDs of the outdoor AMA motocrosses?
